# ========================
# Authors
# ========================

### Create Author
POST http://localhost:3000/api/authors
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "J.K. Rowling",
  "bio": "Author of Harry Potter series"
}

### Get All Authors
GET http://localhost:3000/api/authors

### Get Author by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/authors/1

### Update Author
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/authors/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bio": "British author, philanthropist"
}

### Delete Author
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/authors/2

