# ========================
# Books
# ========================

### Create Book with Existing Author & Genre IDs
POST http://localhost:3000/api/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Harry Potter and the Philosopher's Stone",
  "authorId": 2,
  "publishedYear": 1997,
  "genreIds": [1]
}

### Create Book with New Author & Genres
POST http://localhost:3000/api/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "New Book Example",
  "author": { "name": "wow" },
  "description": "This is the book description",
  "publishedYear": 2025,
  "genres": [{ "name": "Adventure" }, { "name": "Mystery" }]
}

### Get All Books
GET http://localhost:3000/api/books

### Get Book by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/books/5

### Update Book (Change Title, Author, and Genres)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/books/3
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Harry Potter - Updated",
  "author": { "name": "Updated Author" },
  "genres": [{ "name": "Fantasy" }, { "name": "Magic" }]
}

### Delete Book
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/books/1
